# GRAPHICS::GET_TIMECYCLE_TRANSITION_MODIFIER_INDEX

## Returns
* **INT**

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Returns the currently set timecycle modifier's index, or -1 if none is set. This index is purely unformative.
